value.name: High Speed Chase Ends in Wayne County
value.description: A LAUDERDALE COUNTY MAN WAS ARRESTED LATE LAST WEEK FOLLOWING A HIGHSPEED CHASE THAT ENDED IN WAYNE COUNTY. MEDIA SOURCES REPORT, MEMBERS OF THE WAYNE COUNTY SHERIFF'S OFFICE AND WAYNESBORO POLICE DEPARTMENT WERE ALERTED BY THE DECATUR COUNTY SHERIFF'S OFFICE ON FRIDAY THAT THEY WERE ATTEMPTING TO STOP A STOLEN 2004 GMC SIERRA.
